title: Amazingly Fast Drip Irrigation Installer machine.

tasks.task: Cut the breaking off lass and page with a pan.
subtasks: Grip the lass and page with both hands.
Hold the pan firmly.
Position the pan over the lass and page.
Move the pan down sharply to cut the lass and page.
Pick up the pan.
Walk towards the partner.
Hand the pan to the partner.
Accept the pan from the partner.
Walk to the new location.
Prepare for the next task.
